Hi @Dessix, I didn't undestand why you could get same collection with diferent type. LiteCollection.Database was the same reference of initial LiteDatabase instance. Now, in v2, LiteCollection doesnt need LiteDatabase anymore, because uses only DbEngine (a new low layer of database). In DbEngine there is not strong type entity classes, only `BsonDocument`. But you can still use:

```
var db = new LiteDatabase("...");
var col1 = db.GetCollection<Customer>("customer");
var col2 = db.GetCollection<Person>("customer");
var col3 = db.GetCollection("customer"); // same as GetCollection<BsonDocument>()
